## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run validate` inside the `functions` directory after every major domain swap to ensure TypeScript types correctly align with the `firestore.run` wrapper.

### Manual Verification
- Manually trigger [claimCanvasSandbox](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/functions/src/orchestrator/canvas.ts#47-98) locally using the emulator to verify that a Sandbox Canvas successfully transitions from `public` to a claimed `orgId` via `firestore.run`.
- (Optional) Use `npm test` or the interactive test scripts like [canvas-ai-stress-test.ts](file:///Users/cristiankalexai/Progetti/standlo.com/src/scripts/canvas-ai-stress-test.ts) to ensure end-to-end functionality remains intact.
